These files is configuration of PXE: 
default is menu of PXE boot that display in PXE client computer
dhcp.conf is a configuration file of dhcp server (give address by the client)
tftp is a configuration file of tftp server (give kernel and initiral RAM disk (temporary filesystem))
Also you need to install web-serevr, put into it a OS and mention path to OS in PXE boot menu.
Web-server can be Apache, Nginx, NFS
